Package: opendsm
Type: Package
Title: A package for automating a digital soil mapping workflow
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Daniel",
           family = "Saurette",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "daniel.saurette@ontario.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1971-1238")))
Maintainer: Daniel Saurette <daniel.saurette@ontario.ca>
Description: This package contains functions for supporting users
 through a Digital Soil Mapping workflow. Includes functions for
 creating terrain derivatives to be used as covariates, covariate 
 reduction to reduce multicolinearity, sample size determination
 using divergence metrics, and creating predictions using machine
 learning algorithms.
